=head1 Pod-2-DocBook version 1.0

This is a rewrite of Pod::2::DocBook; version 0.6 and earlier were
written by a different author (see L<Pod::2::DocBook/AUTHOR>).

Pod::2::DocBook is a module for translating Pod-formatted documents to
DocBook 4.2 SGML (see L<http://www.docbook.org/>).  The B<pod2docbook>
program is a simple driver for the module.

=head2 Installation

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

=head2 Dependencies

This module requires these other modules:

=over

=item *

Digest::MD5

=item *

Pod::Parser

=item *

Pod::ParseLink

=item *

Text::ParseWords

=item *

Text::Wrap

=back

